# snt
 
 - Rob invented it while a post doc for Dan
 - I did my PhD dissertation on it
 - We used it for amplifier noise metrology with Clarke group
 - We then used it at NIST to measure the amplifiers made in Joe Aumentado's group
 -  KRISS
 - Science projects
 - Joe's ongoing efforts to distribute for free
 - Making a fully dedicated free shot noise network centered on my life as an itinerant quantum noise metrologist

